headline.print_headline: Napolitano Ready to Lead US Delegation to Sochi
headline.main: Napolitano Ready to Lead US Delegation to Sochi

lead_paragraph: Janet Napolitano is ready for the Sochi Winter Olympics focus to turn from concerns about security and the threats of terrorism to all of the special athletes involved.
